---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Vértice-MAXIMUS"
  description="Privacy Policy for Vértice-MAXIMUS - First Conscious Cyber-Organism"
>
  <div class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: October 28, 2025</p>

      <section>
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Vértice-MAXIMUS ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy.
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information
          when you use our open-source cybersecurity platform.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>2.1 Usage Data</h3>
        <p>
          When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain information about
          your device, including information about your web browser, IP address, time zone,
          and some of the cookies that are installed on your device.
        </p>

        <h3>2.2 Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          We use privacy-friendly analytics (Plausible) that does not use cookies and
          complies with GDPR, CCPA, and PECR. No personal data is collected.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Improve and optimize our website and platform</li>
          <li>Understand how visitors use our services</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about updates and security advisories</li>
          <li>Provide technical support</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Open Source Commitment</h2>
        <p>
          Vértice-MAXIMUS is 100% open source. All code is publicly available on GitHub
          under the MIT License. You can audit our code to verify our privacy practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> Code hosting and collaboration</li>
          <li><strong>Plausible Analytics:</strong> Privacy-friendly website analytics</li>
        </ul>
        <p>These services have their own privacy policies governing their use of your information.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your
          personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is
          100% secure.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to data processing</li>
          <li>Data portability</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our service is not directed to individuals under the age of 13. We do not
          knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of
          any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the
          "Last updated" date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@vertice-maximus.com">privacy@vertice-maximus.com</a></li>
          <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/JuanCS-Dev/V-rtice/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Create an issue</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    background: var(--gradient-dark);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  p {
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  ul {
    list-style: disc;
    margin-left: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  li {
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition-base);
  }

  a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-secondary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
  }
</style>
